animeTitle: Kensaku to Enjin no Happy Birthday
animeDescription: An entirely 3DCG Happy Birthday episode of Kensaku to Enjin. It was meant to congratulate the viewer's birthday rather than it being the birthday/anniversary of the Kensaku to Enjin franchise or Yahoo! who owns the franchise.
animeRelated: ['Parent story: Kensaku to Enjin no ABC Days']
